          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript for private or public use and consultation in rites and ceremonies for a set of three sacrifices performed at the beginning of each cycle (season) of four months (cāturmāsya) of the year. Text includes rites for venerating one's ancestors and for purification of the sacrificer. Manuscript is incomplete and lacks an ending.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Cāturmāsya</title>
              <title type="vernacular">चातुर्मास्य</title>
